		<td><b>ppu addressing range</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />when the ppu does its 4 fetches for each tile, is each one able to address anywhere in the ppu range or would is each fetch limited to a specific range.  i was looking at changing my ppu code alitte.  i was wondering if it were possible by writing to the ppu to change a counter, not during normal operation.
<br />
<br />for example
<br />
<br />the name table is fetched from 0x2000 - 0x3000.   is it possible to have the name table fetch from 0x1012 ?
<br />
<br />like wise with the palette and pattern table
<br />
<br />thanks
<br />
<br />matt

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


