	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Pattern table reads have to come from $0000-$0FFF or $1000-$1FFF - the page selected depends on the bits in $2000.
<br />
<br />Nametable reads must come from $2000-$2FFF, since it simply uses the active 'VRAM address' (which stores fine Y scroll in the upper bits), ANDs it with $FFF, then ORs it with $2000.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


